{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-6","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 6","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U prethodnom koraku, postavili ste elemente za <code>h1</code>, <code>h2</code>, komentare i <code>p</code> unutar elementa <code>main</code>. Ovo se zove <em>uklapanje</em>. Ugnježdeni elementi treba da budu postavljeni dva mesta više sa desne strane nego elementa u kojem su ugnježđeni. Ovaj razmak se zove separator i koristi se za čineње da je HTML lak za čitanje.</p>\n<p>Ovo je primer indentacije i prekida linije:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;main>\n  &#x3C;h1>Most important content of the document&#x3C;/h1>\n  &#x3C;p>Some more important content...&#x3C;/p>\n&#x3C;/main>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Element za <code>h1</code>, element za <code>h2</code> i komentari su prelomljeni sa dva razmaka više nego element za <code>main</code> u kodu koji je dole. Koristite taster za razmak (space bar) na vašoj tastaturi da dodate dva razmaka ispred elementa <code>p</code> kako bi i on pravilno prelomio liniju.</p>\n</section>","id":"5dc23991f86c76b9248c6eb8","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-6"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n      <!-- TODO: Add link to cat photos -->\n    <p>Everyone loves cute cats online!</p>\n    </main>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[2,9],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Tvoj kod treba da sadrži element <code>h2</code> sa tekstom <code>Cat Photos</code>. Možda si ga slučajno obrisao, nedostaju početna ili završna oznaka ili je tekst izmenjen.</p>","testString":"assert(\n  document.querySelector('h2') &&\n    code.match(/<\\/h2\\>/) &&\n    document.querySelector('h2').innerText.toLowerCase() === 'cat photos'\n);"},{"text":"<p>Ne biste trebali dodavati elemente od <code>ul</code> ili <code>li</code> iz primera.</p>","testString":"assert(\n  !document.querySelector('ul') && !document.querySelector('li')\n);"},{"text":"<p>Ne smete menjati prekid linije na redu koji sadrži vaš element <code>h2</code>. Njegova oznaka za otvaranje treba da počinje na poziciji 6 od početka reda. Možete ponovo pokrenuti ovaj korak kako biste vratili originalni prekid linije.</p>","testString":"assert(code.toLowerCase().match(/<\\/h1\\>\\s*\\n\\s{6}<h2>/));"},{"text":"<p>Vaš kod bi trebalo da ima komentare. Izbrisali ste komentare iz prethodnog koraka.</p>","testString":"assert(code.match(/<!--.*-->/));"},{"text":"<p>Tekst komentara treba da bude <code>TODO: Add link to cat photos</code>. Ne menjajte tekst ili lokaciju komentara.</p>","testString":"assert(code.match(/<!--\\s*todo:\\s+add\\s+link\\s+to\\s+cat\\s+photos\\.?\\s*-->/i));"},{"text":"<p>Ne treba da menjaš uvlačenje reda sa elementom komentara. Njegova početna oznaka treba da počinje šest razmaka od početka reda. Možeš da resetuješ ovaj korak kako bi vratio originalno uvlačenje.</p>","testString":"assert(\n  code\n    .toLowerCase()\n    .match(/<\\/h2>\\s*\\n\\s{6}<!--\\s*todo:\\s+add\\s+link\\s+to\\s+cat\\s+photos\\s*-->/)\n);"},{"text":"<p>Tvoj kod treba da sadrži element <code>p</code>. Obrisao si element <code>p</code> iz prethodnog koraka.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelector('p'));"},{"text":"<p>Sadržaj elementa <code>p</code> bi trebalo da bude <code>Everyone loves cute cats online!</code>. Ne menjajte tekst, razmak ili formatiranje elementa <code>p</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(\n  document\n    .querySelector('p')\n    .innerText.toLowerCase(),\n    /everyone\\s+loves\\s+cute\\s+cats\\s+online!$/\n);"},{"text":"<p>Početna oznaka elementa <code>p</code> treba da ima isto uvlačenje kao elementi <code>h2</code> i komentar. Njegova početna oznaka treba da počinje šest razmaka od početka reda.</p>","testString":"assert(code.toLowerCase().match(/-->\\s*\\n\\s{6}<p>/));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/#learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","dashedName":"step-6","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-7","prevChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-5","id":"5dc23991f86c76b9248c6eb8","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>CatPhotoApp</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Form</h2>\n        <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>Is your cat an indoor or outdoor cat?</legend>\n            <label><input id=\"indoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"indoor\" checked> Indoor</label>\n            <label><input id=\"outdoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>What's your cat's personality?</legend>\n            <label for=\"loving\"><input id=\"loving\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"loving\" checked> Loving</label>\n            <label for=\"lazy\"><input id=\"lazy\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"lazy\"> Lazy</label>\n            <label for=\"energetic\"><input id=\"energetic\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"energetic\"> Energetic</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"catphotourl\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\n          <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n        </form>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n      <p>\n        No Copyright - <a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org\">freeCodeCamp.org</a>\n      </p>\n    </footer>\n  </body>\n</html>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-6"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}